Bull and Bear Group A said it loweredits monthly dividends on three of its funds.    It said it lowered its Tax Free Income Fund &lt;BLTFX> to 10.3cts from 10.6 cts; its U.S. Government Guaranteed SecuritiesFund &lt;BBUSX> to 11.5 cts from 11.8 cts; and its High Yield Fund&lt;BULHX> to 14 cts from 14.2 cts.    All dividends are payable March 31 to shareholders ofrecord March 25, the company said. Reuter&#3;